Skill Development: build an understanding of communications and marketing practices tools and strategies used through social medias channels, learn how to collaborate across departments, learn how an individual's work feeds into the greater goals of a large organization.
Workplace Experience & Belonging: learn how to collaborate, take and implement feedback, share ideas and contribute to a team in a professional environment with tight deadlines. Contribute student perspective to the various video projects and express the collective student voice through drafted scripts.
